<sect2 id='gimp-layer-transparency-menu' lang="en;de;fr;zh_CN">
  <title>
    <phrase lang="en">Transparency</phrase>
    <phrase lang="de">Das Untermenü <quote>Transparenz</quote></phrase>
    <phrase lang="fr">Transparence</phrase>
    <phrase lang="zh_CN">透明</phrase>
  </title>

  <figure>
    <title>
      <phrase lang='en'>The Transparency submenu of the Layer menu</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Das Untermenü <quote>Transparenz</quote></phrase>
      <phrase lang='fr'>Le sous-menu Transparence du menu Calque</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">图层菜单透明子菜单</phrase>
    </title>
    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject lang="en;de">
        <imagedata fileref='../images/menus/menus-layer-transparency.png'
          format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>
      <imageobject lang="fr">
        <imagedata fileref='../images/menus/fr/menus-layer-transparency.png'
        format="PNG"/> 
      </imageobject>
      <imageobject lang="zh_CN">
        <imagedata
          fileref='../images/menus/zh_CN/menus-layer-transparency.png'
          format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>
    </mediaobject>
  </figure>

  <para lang='en'>
    The Transparency submenu of the Layers menu contains operations that
    use or affect the alpha channel of the active layer. 
  </para>
  <para lang="de">
    In diesem Untermenü finden Sie verschiedene Kommandos, um mit dem Alphakanal,
    also der Transparenz der Ebene, zu arbeiten.
  </para>
  <para lang='fr'>
    Le sous-menu Transparence du menu Calque contient les commandes 
    concernant le canal Alpha du calque actif.
  </para>
  <para lang="zh_CN">
    图层菜单的透明子菜单包括一些使用或影响活动图层 Alpha 通道的操作。
  </para>

  <sect3 lang="en;de">
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">Activate submenü</phrase>
      <phrase lang="cs">Aktivace dialogu</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Aufruf des Untermenüs</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Activer le Dialogue</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">开启对话框</phrase>
    </title>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang='en'>
          You can accede to it via 
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>Layer</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem>Transparency</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          Das Untermenü kann aus dem Bildfenster erreicht werden:
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>E</accel>bene</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem>Tr<accel>a</accel>sparenz</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>

  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang='en;fr;zh_CN'>Transparency Menuitems</phrase>
      <phrase lang='de'>Der Inhalt des Untermenüs</phrase>
    </title>
    
    <para lang="de">
      Im Untermenü <guilabel>Transparenz</guilabel> stehen Ihnen folgende
      Kommandos zur Verfügung:
    </para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-alpha-add" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="plug-in-threshold-alpha" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-color-to-alpha" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-alpha-semi-flatten" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-alpha-selection-replace" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem >
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-alpha-selection-add" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-alpha-selection-subtract" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-alpha-selection-intersect" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>
</sect2>
